{
  "text": "Functional products in the form of gels deliver equally well as hydrophilic and hydrophobic substances into the body. The number of active components is unlimited and typically gel products are multi-component composition [CITATION_1] . Thickeners play a role not only of supporting components, but they are biologically active, having a beneficial effect on the human body.",
